headline: Trip.com (TCOM) Lags Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Trip.com (TCOM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -4.65% and 0.25%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
